      "title": "SLPP reforms group want President to resign",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The reforms group of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna has called on President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to resign immediately, given the present situation in the country.",
        "The statement further says that they believe that an all-party government should be formed with the participation of all the members of parliament who agree within a certain time frame under a suitable prime minister.",
        "Sri Lanka: Navy ships with unidentified persons left Colombo Port"
      ],
